3: All gone... Humans... have they all left?
Activating repair sequence—
It's fixed... My body... wow...
But... why aren't I corrupted...?
Just now, when I wasn't thinking straight, I kept thinking about the time with Mommy and Daddy...
It's because of them that... I... persevered...
But... I can never go back...
Humans will not accept the machine that is me...
But... I'm thinking like a human now... and free...
So... am I a human... or... a machine...?
Ah!
This is... my... digital diary...!
I must keep it safe...
Relaying data—
Mother, Father... Jane... I'll keep myself safe... I'll bring all these precious things over...
Then... I'll continue to walk this Earth... as a new me.
Even though I don't know what the future holds... Or where I should go...
But now that I've accepted my true self... I don't know why, but I feel a sense of relief... Heehee...
From now on, I'm my own person...
It's a bit lonely though, hehe...
